    DirectHF             As Long    ' [in/out] -10000, 0,     0,       relative direct path level at high frequencies (win32/xbox) '
    Room                 As Long    ' [in/out] -10000, 1000,  0,       room effect level (at low and mid frequencies) (win32/xbox) '
